text: Eulimnadia is a genus of branchiopods in the family Limnadiidae. There are about 13 described species in Eulimnadia. ==Species== * Eulimnadia agassizii Packard, 1874 * Eulimnadia antillarum (Baird, 1852) * Eulimnadia antlei Mackin, 1940 * Eulimnadia astraova Belk, 1989 * Eulimnadia cylindrova Belk, 1989 * Eulimnadia diversa Mattox, 1937 * Eulimnadia francescae * Eulimnadia inflecta * Eulimnadia oryzae * Eulimnadia stoningtonensis * Eulimnadia texana (Packard, 1871) * Eulimnadia thompsoni * Eulimnadia ventricosa ==References== ==Further reading== * Category:Diplostraca
